  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3600441">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3600441/" class="title-link">敬仰：海青舞，风影楼</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3600441"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3935446/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3935446-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3935446/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">洛小贼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-27"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-27 16:33:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3600441_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  海青舞，只有风影楼才配。如果过身临其境，也就只有成为雷洪飞一样只剩喜欢、敬仰。  如果书中所述已经成为事实，我辈安可稍事休息。可是，那还不存在，所以我辈仍需努力。  如果真的存在那么一片热土，那么就算飞蛾扑火，我也会去，义无反顾，就算粉身碎骨。亦然。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
