  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4572632">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4572632/" class="title-link">不喜欢！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4572632"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/30398097/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/30398097/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">时时好好晴晴</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-10"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-10 12:06:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4572632_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不喜欢作者的写作风格！感觉作者一直在做激情演讲报告！强迫读者去感受他的感受。很是虚夸，不实在也不真实。作者似乎只活在他臆想的世界中，脱离现实！同样的军事体裁作品：《兵王》《国之利刃》的写作手法稳重实在得多！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4572632/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
